+# Plan
+
+## Backend
+
+- Add a lightweight forecast DTO containing `dueInDays` and `count`.
+- Add a forecast list to `DueMemoryTrackers`.
+- Populate forecasts in `RecallService.getDueMemoryTrackers` by counting the same `getMemoryTrackersNeedToRepeat` query for windows `0`, `3`, `7`, and `14`.
+- Add targeted controller/service coverage for monotonic counts and active tracker filtering.
+
+## Frontend
+
+- Store recall forecast counts in `useRecallData`.
+- Update `RecallPage` to save forecasts from recall responses and render them on done-state load-more buttons.
+- Keep button actions and treadmill progress logic unchanged.
+- Update API fixture/generated local types and focused page tests.
+
+## Validation
+
+- Run the required backend command:
+  `cmd /c "backend\gradlew.bat -p backend test --tests com.odde.doughnut.services.RecallServiceWithSpacedRepetitionAlgorithmTest -Dspring.profiles.active=test --build-cache --parallel"`
+- Run targeted frontend tests if practical.
+
